<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN276-intro">tiṇai, atu; tuṟai, tāṉainilai. maturaip pūtaṉiḷanākaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN276">
<l>naṟuvirai tuṟanta naraiveṇ kūnta</l>
<l>liraṅkā ḻaṉṉa tiraṅkukaṇ vaṟumulaic</l>
<l>cemmutu peṇṭiṉ kātalañ ciṟāaṉ</l>
<l>maṭappā lāymakaḷ vaḷḷukirt teṟitta</l>
<l>kuṭappāṟ cilluṟai pōlap</l>
<l>paṭaikkunō yellān tāṉā yiṉaṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The beloved little son of the upright old woman</l>
<l>with grey-white tresses that had abandoned fragrant scents</l>
<l>[and] empty breasts with nipples shrunken like Iram kernels,</l>
<l>like a few drops [of buttermilk] into the the milk in the pot</l>
<l>that leapt from the sharp nails of the cowherd girl whose share is youth</l>
<l>he became the whole bane of the army.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
